data.database_description: This database schema is designed to manage information related to educational courses, their authors/tutors, students, and student performance. It includes tables for storing details about course authors and tutors, student profiles, available subjects, specific courses, student enrollments in those courses, and test results taken by students. The relationships between these entities are established through foreign keys, ensuring data integrity and allowing for comprehensive querying of the educational system's operations and outcomes.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each author or tutor.
A code representing the author or tutor's status or type.
The username used by the author or tutor to log in.
The password for the author or tutor's account.
The first name of the author or tutor.
The middle name of the author or tutor.
The last name of the author or tutor.
Indicates the gender of the author or tutor (0 for female, 1 for male).
The first line of the address for the author or tutor.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores information about course authors and tutors, including their login credentials and personal details.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each student.
Date when the student registered in the system.
Date of the last time the student logged into the system.
Username used by the student to log in.
Password for the student's account.

Middle name of the student, if applicable.
Last name or surname of the student.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores information about students, including their registration details and personal data.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each subject.
Name of the subject, e.g., Computer Science, Arts, Language.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores information about different subjects available in the educational system.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for each course.
References the author or tutor of the course.
References the subject to which the course belongs.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores details about various courses, including their names, descriptions, and associations with authors and subjects.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for the student course enrollment record.
Identifier for the student enrolled in the course.

Date and time when the student enrolled in the course.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores details about student enrollments in courses, including enrollment and completion dates.

columns.columnDescription: Unique identifier for the student course enrollment record associated with the test.

enriched_schema.tableDescription: Stores information about tests taken by students, including the date of the test and the result.
